[h1]Allows hammers and axes to auto-fire while still benefitting from racial buffs.[/h1]

This mod is required in order to restore full functionality of both mods. Requires [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=763259329]Frackin' Races[/url] and [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782921923]Windup Weapons Auto-fire[/url] to work.

Check out Argle Bargles [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=787655233]Easier Hammers and Axes[/url] or my own [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=782911333]Windup Weapons Glow[/url] for other windup options.

