Allows hammers and axes to auto-fire while still benefitting from racial buffs.

This mod is required in order to restore full functionality of both mods. Requires [url=community.playstarbound.com/resources/3717/]Frackin' Races[/url] and [url=community.playstarbound.com/resources/4283/]Windup Weapons Auto-fire[/url] to work.

